vote.title: Authorize an Interlocal Agreement in the amount of $2,824,600.00 with Dallas County on behalf of the Dallas County Health and Human Services to provide scattered site housing assistance for persons with HIV/AIDS for the period October 1, 2023 through September 30, 2024 - Not to exceed $2,824,600.00 - Financing: U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development Housing Opportunities for Persons with AIDS Grant Funds
